title: Anth
subTitle: Kali, the son of a gangster, rapes and kills Pooja, and frames her fiance, who is killed in custody, for the crime. As a result, her brother, Vijay, vows revenge against Kali.

title: Zulm Ka Badla
subTitle: Verma adopts Geeta, the orphaned daughter of his friend, who grows up to marry his son, Anil. However, when a gangster dies during Anil's probe, both men suspect that Geeta is responsible.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Daata
subTitle: A decorated school teacher's life is upended by devastating rumours, which ultimately leads to his death. His son Kundan now seeks vengeance.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Gumrah
subTitle: Seeing Roshni's talent for singing, Rahul gives her a break and they eventually fall in love. On a foreign trip, she is arrested for possession of cocaine, not knowing that it is all Rahul's doing.

title: Vinashak
subTitle: A diligent and determined police officer is tasked with uncovering the truth behind a crooked warden involved in illicit weapon trafficking.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Khoobsurat
subTitle: Sanju, a kind mn owes a smuggler a lot of money which puts him and Gudia, an orphan, in a trivial position. Later, he poses as an NRI in front of a family to swindle money.

title: Khoobsurat
subTitle: Sanju, a kind mn owes a smuggler a lot of money which puts him and Gudia, an orphan, in a trivial position. Later, he poses as an NRI in front of a family to swindle money.

title: Chintu Ji
subTitle: Rishi, the son of a legendary actor, decides to enter politics and go to Hadbahedi, a remote village. However, he creates havoc by misleading the villagers who trust him simply because he is famous.

title: Naagin Bani Suhaagan
subTitle: Vaishali, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, is blessed with a boon to transform herself into a shapeshifting snake. She falls into a dilemma when circumstances force her to go against her love.

title: Nastik
subTitle: A young Shankar is devasted when Tiger kills his entire family. He turns into an atheist, blaming God for his misfortune and sets off to seek revenge on Tiger.

title: Mohra
subTitle: After a journalist helps to release him from prison, a man agrees to work as a hitman for her, leading him to entangle with a battle between two drug lords.

title: Bumm Bumm Bole
subTitle: An idealist elder brother lands in a dilemma after he misplaces his little sister's shoes. Unable to afford a new pair, the siblings agree to share the shoes, leading to several escapades.

title: Singham Returns
subTitle: Bajirao Singham, an honest police officer, encounters Babaji, a god-man with connections to high profile politicians, when he investigates the death of an officer from his team.

title: Vardi
subTitle: Constable Bhagwan is killed by Lalchand, a gangster. Years later, Bhagwan's son Ajay, along with his father's close associate Inspector Verma, tries to capture Lalchand and bring him to justice.

title: Housefull
subTitle: Aarush is an unlucky man and carries his bad luck wherever he goes. His quest to find love only makes his life more miserable as he ends up in complicated situations.

title: Housefull
subTitle: Aarush is an unlucky man and carries his bad luck wherever he goes. His quest to find love only makes his life more miserable as he ends up in complicated situations.

title: Inquilaab
subTitle: A politician helps a jobless man become a police officer and then uses him for his nefarious activities. After his wife finds out he is being used as a pawn, she tries to change his ways.

title: Sauda
subTitle: Jyoti and Deepak fall in love and get married to each other. However, due to several misunderstandings and financial troubles, they get separated.

title: Action Jackson
subTitle: After falling love with a clumsy girl, a small-time goon comes in contact with his doppelganger, AJ, before setting off on a romantic journey with his ladylove.

title: Happy New Year
subTitle: Shuffling between old grudges and new grooves, Charlie and his friends bumble their way through an international dance competition to break into a heavily guarded vault of diamonds.

title: Talaash: The Hunt Begins
subTitle: Arjun grows up to be a high-profile vigilante after his father's murder and sister's abduction. Soon, he vows revenge and sets out on a mission to find his sister.

title: Himmatwala
subTitle: After being humiliated by an autocratic landlord, a temple priest kills himself. Later, the priest's son returns to the village seeking revenge.

title: Bhagam Bhaag
subTitle: A drama troupe flies to London for a performance. However, things take a tragic turn when three members of their team are falsely accused of murder.

title: Ganga Ki Saugand
subTitle: Thakur Jaswant Singh, a tyrannical village landlord, assaults Jeeva's mother and has him thrown out of the village. Jeeva returns as a dacoit in order to take revenge.
